      <title>致命的俄罗斯滑翔炸弹袭击哈尔科夫邮政分拣中心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/war-in-ukraine-deadly-russian-glide-bomb-hits-postal-hub-in-kharkiv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一架俄罗斯战机向哈尔科夫发射了一枚滑翔炸弹，造成邮政枢纽至少一名平民死亡，乌克兰第二大城市继续遭受频繁的空袭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/war-in-ukraine-deadly-russian-glide-bomb-hits-postal-hub-in-kharkiv</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 16:59:23 GMT</pubDate>
