    <item>
      <title>特朗普是总统还是普通公民：为什么最高法院的豁免裁决是一项考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/supreme-court-immunity-decision-could-save-trump-in-2020-election-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院将于周一就唐纳德·特朗普的说法作出裁决，特朗普称自己不会因试图推翻 2020 年大选结果而受到刑事指控，该案件很有可能被退回下级法院进行进一步的法律争论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/supreme-court-immunity-decision-could-save-trump-in-2020-election-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>毛里塔尼亚总统加祖阿尼以 56% 的得票率有望避免决选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/mauritania-president-ghazouani-set-to-avoid-a-runoff-election-with-56-of-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据这个西北非洲国家选举当局的初步结果，穆罕默德·乌尔德·加祖阿尼有望在周六的选举中连任毛里塔尼亚总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/mauritania-president-ghazouani-set-to-avoid-a-runoff-election-with-56-of-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 15:21:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民意调查显示选民担忧 拜登党内盟友关系趋于紧密</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/top-biden-party-allies-close-ranks-as-poll-signals-voter-concern</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项民意调查显示，拜登上周在与唐纳德·特朗普的辩论中表现不佳，这让更多美国人对总统的领导能力产生了怀疑，因此民主党核心人士纷纷支持拜登竞选连任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/top-biden-party-allies-close-ranks-as-poll-signals-voter-concern</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 14:36:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非总统将于周日宣布联合内阁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/south-african-president-to-announce-new-cabinet-on-sunday-night</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨 (Cyril Ramaphosa) 将于周日宣布新的联合内阁名单。一个多月前，他所在的政党在选举中失去了议会多数席位，这是该党执政 30 年来首次。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/south-african-president-to-announce-new-cabinet-on-sunday-night</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 14:06:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
